				<td colspan="2"><span>No instrument modifiers (aside from AA skills) stack.
<br />

<br />
If you have Wind Instrument tribute, you are not required to wield/wear and instrument/item with a wind modifier to play invis.
<br />

<br />
The same applies to the other instrument tributes... ie: dont have to use a drum to play HOS if you have percussion tribute..
<br />
